<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I usually write a review describing my personal experience. I typically avoid binary rating system (only 1 or 5 stars, no in between) If someone looks<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I usually write a review describing my personal experience. I typically avoid binary rating system (only 1 or 5 stars, no in between) If someone looks at my ratings and reviews of previous books and finds something they agree with, then they can drawn their own conclusion if they like the same books as me.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
